Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Isumi, what do you say \Nto being lost for one more night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we become separated now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a chance we may never \Nmeet again in this lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only came to school, \Nwe could see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:49.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She has friends to invite her \Nto school like that, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:56.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something so that \Nthe Miss can enjoy going to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose is the meaning of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I need to answer that immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I think the testament of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is not something \Nthat is given to you by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having been born a human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there must be a way \Nof life that's more true to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this going to take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While she's coming up \Nwith excuses like that, it'll be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:31.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when urgently needing \Nto go to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,you listen to what the Miss has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:36.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is yet another part of a butler's duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no filming allowed within the residence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:49.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is there to support his \Nmistress in all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:57.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:01.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about a boy who fights \Nand puts his life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:05.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not, by any means, \Nwatch this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:18.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:18.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:25.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:25.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:28.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:28.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:33.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:33.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:41.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:41.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:56.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:56.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:03:02.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:03:02.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:09.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:14.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:14.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:21.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:21.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:28.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:28.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim Essaim. \NMr. Cow, Mr. Cow! What is it, Mr. Frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss! It's Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? It's so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dummy! What \Nare you doing all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will help you change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it would be a shame \Nto only accompany you to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I do something embarrassing \Nlike change in front of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accompany me to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I shall be \Nescorting you to and from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think a trick like that \Nwill make me go to school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:47.30,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}*This is within the grounds of the Sanzenin estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, no need to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be fine to just go \Nsomewhere to have fun like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:43.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? \NA student's duty is to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please attend every day and study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:55.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}*This is within the grounds of Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see you later, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go to school, we become \Nseparated for the duration,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why do you want me \Nto go to school so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some who can't go to school \Nanymore, even if they want to, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall come \Nfor you again after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Miss away at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we really get some peace \Nand quiet here at the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the tiger would refrain from talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'd have even more peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler-in-debt sure is coldhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, don't you need to be in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were technically in high school \Nbefore you came here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be the Miss's butler here \Nfor another 40 years to repay my debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so given that, going to school just seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've got another eternity of lectures \Nthat remind me of crappy games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't the blackboard have \Nthe ability to skip forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they continue to adhere \Nto such old-fashioned systems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that education in Japan is never going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so rare for you to know \Nwhen we're going in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't attend \Nschool every day for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the reason, but I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sinner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was one letter off...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she forgot a notebook at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when \NI make a rare excursion to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is because you go to school \Nso infrequently that this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have dedicated yourself \Nto studying all day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow the fruit of that labor \Nto languish in a deserted classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's quite late already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I get into school at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious individual sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that suspicious individual \Nfrom some time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's also a Sanzenin family butler, \Nwho also saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you are a teacher here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, what're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dodging your blow from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out in the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on so-called night duty. \NYou know, night duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hard work is much appreciated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect. Miss Nagi apparently \Nforgot something here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to ask this, but might \NI borrow the key to the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The key to the classroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, you're coming \Nto the night duty room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I don't want you \Nto trouble yourself, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait, I'll go get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:34.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Duty Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will go myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just open the door...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This night duty room is rather bursting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the lifestyle sensibilities \Nof a woman in her mid-20s, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already culled a lot of my \Npersonal belongings, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It can't be helped, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford rent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bath in the night duty room \Nis cleaner and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait, you're an outsider! \NI don't have to take this from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsy's bringing a man back \Nwith her to the night duty room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a younger guy to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scandal exposed! You'll be fired for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but that! My salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that look of poverty... \NI feel like I've seen it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a butler of the Sanzenin family. \NMy name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trespassed on school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after making a pass \Nat the student body president,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you took a kick to the face \Nand got rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you tried to kidnap and confine her \Nto the student council office,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your plot was foiled by Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That butler of the Sanzenin family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like some rather erroneous \Nembellishments have been added to the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I'm the student council committee chairman, Izumi Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, vice chairman, Miki Hanabishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciplinary committee member, Risa Asakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, these people \Nare Miss Katsura's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um... Hayata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm "Hayate".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick up something Miss Nagi forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Incidentally, we are here to study \Nfor our midterms, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed we are, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, just call me "Hayata".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But meeting for a study group \Nso late at night at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are studious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we truly were studious,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't be meeting \Nfor a study group, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Hakuou \Nis a prestigious school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that a portion \Nof our students are super smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who transfer \Nand skip grades, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fundamentally, except \Nunder extreme circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our system of automatic \Nadvancement won't flunk you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school covers grades 1-12!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Students like us, who've \Nbeen here since grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are stupid, as it should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that we're on the verge of flunking \Ndue to extreme circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I'm tutoring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way Katsy teaches makes \Nthings so easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good example of how good athletes \Ndon't always make good coaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. I was mocking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mock your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The classroom key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return it when you're done, okay, Hayata?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura, you know what \Nmy real name is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, you sure \Naren't a boy for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the classroom \Nin the West Building so late at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, surely, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is an old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are apparently a lot of appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring back any curses \Nor anything with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Sadako or Kayako \Nor Jason or Freddy show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beat them up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because they don't have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's the school building \Nthey attend on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way any such things will appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Isn't this way different than \Nwhen I was here last?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, since I'm here anyway, I guess I'll go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this red door...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Old School Building Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like some squid? (Ika wa ikaga)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have lots, thanks. \N(Gattsuri itadaki-masu)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I got one from Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the school building right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To what do I owe this sudden phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, school at night can be dangerous in various ways, so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. I'm relieved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were alone, \Nbut I hear lots of other people around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess you're there \Nwith a bunch of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hear a lot of chatter \Nin the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like this is a test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's necessary for them \Nto be screaming like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?! Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(234.,41)}No Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(18.667,198.9)}Do it over from somewhere\N with a good signal. \NIn fact, do over your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I better hurry to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taking him a while to come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at night, classrooms hold \Nalluring recorders and P.E. clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are distracting for adolescent boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a butler, but he's still a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably ransacking Hina's desk right \Nabout now and has her recorder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having an awful lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Miss Student Body President...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a special effort to bring you snacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are you working seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are seriously discussing \Nthe perverted actions of adolescent boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In conclusion, your recorder must be \Nin Hayata's possession right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious and study! Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe Hayata's mistakenly \Nwandered into the old school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old school building?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a distinct possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible. That place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hakuou Academy \Nis haunted by evil spirits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hear they appear \Nin the old school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, knowing that school, I'm sure \Nthey'll hire a ghost sweeper or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?! \NIf Hayate mistakenly goes in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, respond! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(248,39)}No Signal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(312,214)}You have no signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate of the Sanzenin family \Nwent to that old school building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're just saying it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know that he's \Nactually wandered in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An outsider may be in danger \Non school grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be ghosts and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Ghosts and stuff \Ndon't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hina for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's my little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's too bad that she's a girl, \Nconsidering how tough she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I said, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I better hurry up and find Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nwhy's it so bright in here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scream just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought ghosts and stuff \Ndo not bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like there's a girl who wouldn't \Nbe bothered by those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say will-o'-the-wisps \Nare a scientific phenomenon called plasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing logical \Nabout what scares you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here is the final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that has been \Nasking you these questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're Miss Katsura, \Nthe student body president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Katsura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go wandering \Ninto scary places like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so this is the old school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder things didn't seem quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened earlier is to be kept \Nstrictly secret, all right, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell anyone that I was scared \Nlike that, I'll hit you for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like you already hit me \Nfor real earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Let us hurry up \Nand get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd ever go home after being beaten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I need to get the Miss's notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overruled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to identify who that \Nbastard was, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait... Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not do to leave things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:53.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura really \Nis the same as Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She absolutely hates to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting kind of hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, are you self-conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're alone with \Na girl at school at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not self-conscious \Nabout someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too unguarded to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn to be \Na bit more modest around boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being easygoing like that, who knows \Nwhat someone might do to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's you, Hayate, \Nyou can do anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! M-Miss Katsura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I played a joke like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would boys think I was being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...around boys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she hated to lose \Nabout as much as the Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She hates to lose even more than the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the doll that I defeated earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Leave, you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, or I-I will eat you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Hinagiku Katsura,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the student body president of Hakuou Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is unfair to execute a sneak attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate, my dear Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up and leave this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean. L-Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The humiliation you made me suffer earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return the favor a hundred times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My dear Hayate"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the situation at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but could this really be a simple \Nscare tactic to get us out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura, let's forget about \Nthat terrifying monster and leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'm defeating this bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can't go until you've magnificently \Ndefeated that terrifying doll?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such a thing! Let us leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fight him without fear, \Nhe's not that tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am real strong, \Nso I will defeat you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have changed your appearance, \Nbut you're no match for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't done anything yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that was incredible, Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You defeated the ghost \Nwith just your fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be what they call "chi"! "Chi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the masters use!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have used it without realizing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're incredible, Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I'm convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now. The evil spirit has been \Ndefeated, so let us hurry and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get Nagi's notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Miss Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they have finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us defeat the real evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried! You didn't get \Npossessed by evil spirits, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:32.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,School really is a nice thing to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,School life is a distant thing for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the butler-in-debt thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is where in the next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:41.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a terrible incident happens \Nthat no one could ever have anticipated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We all will fight against a state of emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:47.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, we have no choice but to fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:57.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:57.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:02.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:02.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:08.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:08.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:17.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:17.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:23.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:23.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:29.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:29.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:33.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:33.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:39.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:39.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:44.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:44.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:55.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:55.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:23:00.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:23:00.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:05.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:05.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:10.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:10.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:14.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:14.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:25.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:25.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, courage. \NI'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we've brought Maria \Non for a guest appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this song is so soothing. \NThat's Maria for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Hayate?! Getting all spoony!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I think I'll train hard \Nto become a soothing ladylike girl, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are best as you are now, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Maria, I recall seeing this \Nscene several times before...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:19.44,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:03.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode takes place \Nduring the same time as Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:06.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we get to see \Ncat-ear Hayate from another angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:08.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:10.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it is a completely \Noriginal story made just for anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:13.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! That makes me feel \Nboth worry and anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:14.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strangest Hyperdeflation Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:17.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Play Your Games \Nand Don't Build Up a Backlog".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:20.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hero, please get fished up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Strangest Hyperdeflation Ever. \NPlay Your Games and Don't Build Up a Backlog
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:23.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rawr! I'm currently intensely fired up!
